  62:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      or HAL_XSPI_Command_IT() functions :
  63:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      (+) Instruction phase : the mode used and if present the size, the instruction
  64:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****          opcode and the DTR mode.
  65:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      (+) Address phase : the mode used and if present the size, the address
  66:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****          value and the DTR mode.
