 110:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      (+) The size of the status bytes, the match value, the mask used, the match mode (OR/AND),
 111:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****          the polling interval and the automatic stop activation.
