 116:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      (+) In interrupt mode, HAL_XSPI_StatusMatchCallback() will be called each time the status matc
