 174:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****     [..]
 175:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      The  purpose of High-speed interface is primary to shift data or data strobe by one quarter of
 176:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      bus clock period, with a correct timing accuracy. DLL must be calibrated versus this clock per
 177:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      The calibration process is automatically enabled when one of the three conditions below is met
 178:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      (+) The XSPI exits Reset state.
 179:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      (+) The Prescaler is set.
 180:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      (+) The configuration of communication is set.
 181:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****     [..]
 182:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      HAL_XSPI_GetDelayValue() function Get the delay values of the high-speed interface DLLs..
 183:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****     [..]
 184:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      HAL_XSPI_SetDelayValue() function Set the delay values of the high-speed interface DLLs..
 185:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c **** 
